data.description: Welcome to your new oasis! This charming 4-bedroom single-story home is nestled in close proximity to the serene Floyd Lamb Tule Springs Park. Step inside and discover a delightful & cheerful home featuring beautiful, recently upgraded soft-close kitchen cabinets in 2019, and bathroom cabinets and floors in 2021. The spacious kitchen showcases elegant granite countertops and a convenient dining island that seamlessly connects to the family room, complete with a vaulted ceiling and sunlit windows, offering a view of the brand-new, heated contemporary pool and spa installed in 2022 in the backyard. Enjoy outdoor gatherings with family and friends on the covered patio, perfect for barbecues or taking a refreshing dip in the pool. The primary bedroom provides a cozy seating nook, and the garage offers ample space with an oversized design. This lovely home is near shopping, dining options, and freeway access. Don't wait to make this house your new home!
